q`, parses unchecked, and passes unvalidated shapes into `validate`, so a single zod/io-ts schema parse at the entry would close all three. Findings 2 and 7 are a paired observability gap: errors and audit events both vanish silently, leaving the failure path undebuggable. Finding 6 is isolated style.\n\n**Verdict scope:** scope: api-correctness"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2885,"cache_read_input_tokens":66346,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2885},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"52104f79-6fc3-4e82-8288-be893a9d3c53","uuid":"091ad580-25df-48db-8190-50d8b4c73903","request_id":"req_011CbqJze5BNjZVqHMUSvbGf"}
